description: Sequence of the remaining nonprimes out of sieve of type: {step 1: starting with the sequence of positive integers A000027; step 2: delete every prime number A000040; step 3: delete every prime(1)-th number greater than the prime(1) from the remaining sequence; step 4: delete every prime(2)-th number greater than the prime(2) from the remaining sequence; etc. for prime(k)-th numbers for k = 3, 4, 5, ...}.
